Part B\
Selection control structure (if then elseif else) warmup\
1. ask user to enter age, and some threshold\
2. depending on the age being above the threshold or not, respond to the user "you are young" / "you are old".\
3. validate user input to reject zero or negative ages.\
4. put this in the body of a loop so that the program does not quit until a positive age is entered.\
5. Redo the elseif versions of the sales commission and tax exercises from vba1 (this can be done as homework)\
